Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic can heal the\Ndried hearts of modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage this time is a resort hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case is a huge three-parter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:57.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron Murder Case (The Murder)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron Murder Case (The Murder).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I in such a hot place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Izu Princess Hotel - Private Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at such a hot time of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because of\Nthe professor's phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Three days and\Ntwo nights at a hotel in Izu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for free, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be out looking for\Nthose men in black who shrunk me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the occasional break is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NYou should come swim, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only half has been paid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Agasa-{\i1}sama{\i0}, party of three,\Ncorrect? There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! Check some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you! Only half\Nof the cost has been paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with paying half then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring that\Nmuch money with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nhe did mention something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really free?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's as good\Nas free in your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case? What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My scientist friends and I like\Nto communicate via PC lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them found an interesting\Ntour on an online forum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and invited me to apply for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the 'Izu Mystery Tour.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, my friend, his granddaughter,\Nand I all were chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his granddaughter caught a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so now I'm offering you our spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six parties will attend--\Nten people in all, including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets a\N50% hotel discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tour organizer is\None of the other seven people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whoever figures out\Nwho that is gets to stay for free
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wins floppy disks\Ncontaining a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's not a program you need...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do I look for\Nthis mysterious organizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received the names and\Nroom numbers of all the attendees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the organizer's supposed\Nto play a certain character
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cause an incident during the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain character?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a character you\Nknow very well from novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Night Baron-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3.04 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how long you took\Nto respond to my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was most informative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Konno Shiro, Room 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Konno Shiro (28) - Bank Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find the Baron that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who\Nanswered in 2.86 seconds--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebara-{\i1}san{\i0}, Room 2101.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebara Tokio (32)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exposing oneself when caught
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:32.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneshiro Gen'ichiro (74)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,off guard is the way of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Shizue-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayashi Shizue (56) - Kaneshiro's Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneshiro-{\i1}san{\i0}, Room 2001...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took you 6.29 seconds to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are bad, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected\Nyou would question me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I'll know the\Ntruth once I process this data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that data's incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still missing\Nsomeone's information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo Hideko (29)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lsn't that right, Night Baron-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that,\NKamijo-{\i1}san {\i0}of Room 2102?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0.97 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add it in after my\N1.48 seconds, Konno-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Baron thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.\NHe's just playin' innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shows up in lots\Nof Shinichi's dad's novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron is an elusive\Nvillain created by my father, Yusaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a thief of the darkness\Nand sometimes a crazed murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father hasn't revealed\Nthe Night Baron's identity yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but whoever's using\Nhis name is one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes no sense.\NI'm going to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! What about the money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. There were\Nsupposed to be ten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only eight here,\Nus three and these five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're missing two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's just your butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like it's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me and fill my drinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Maeda Satoru (30)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Maeda Satoru-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}. Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly hope so! He was\NJapan's karate champ six years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the reason\NI started practicing karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mori Ran!\NI won the recent city championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A karate champ\Nand a city champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to\Nmeet you here! I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you. This is\Nmy fiancé, Sayama Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it personally.\NShe gets jealous easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Night Baron, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 1901, Maeda-{\i1}san{\i0}...\N0.75 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayama-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange. You're supposed to\Nbe two professors and a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't come,\Nso we came in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my father,\Nand he's a detective, not a professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His name is Mori Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they call him a great detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dirty of him to\Nsend a detective instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come now. We have\Nfewer possible Barons now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Mori Kogoro here,\Nwe cannot afford to show our faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like Dad's famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why they were shocked\Nwhen I said Dad was a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's basically like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I find which of those\Nseven is the Night Baron,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we get to enjoy\NIzu Beach for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So that's why Professor\NAgasa told him it was free!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course! Because\Nthere's no mystery I can't solve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just ranting about going\Nhome 'cuz you have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! I better go do\Nmy preliminary questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in such high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we look around the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?\NLet's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay\Nhere a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Well, I'll be in\Nthe gift shop downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll be there in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were they all so shocked\Nat the mention of a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you get is to\Nstay for free, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that murderous glare!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's\Nwhat the professor said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and wins floppy disks\Ncontaining a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's not a program you need...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I can just call him after\Ndinner and get all the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've changed in the\Nrestroom and then taken the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who dressed\Nup as the Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excluding us, there are\Nseven people on this tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The purpose of the tour is to find\Nits organizer among the attendees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organizer who would cause\Nan incident as the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just a simple\Ngame to stay for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd push someone\Noff just for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that program?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Agasa Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. All the ad said was\Nthat it was the 'ultimate program.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me.\NMy professor friend mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something or other about a virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A virus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd, though. He shouldn't\Nknow any more about it than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't tell me that virus is--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! I've been\Nwaiting at the gift shop this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! You're dripping wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh, slipped and fell into the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing to laugh\Nabout! What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't seem hurt.\NGo change and then we'll have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! And Maeda-{\i1}san\N{\i0}and Sayama-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father just\Nfinished interrogating us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're the Night Baron,\Naren't you?!" and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NThat's a lovely dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful. Some dirty-minded\Nwolf might be on the prowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old pervert just doesn't learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}signed you\Nup for this mystery tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's a huge\Nfan of Kudo Yusaku's novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's especially\Nfond of Night Baron ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows more\Nabout the Night Baron than I!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my hairstyle\Nis the same as his!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only\Nexpert on the Night Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that's food for thought.\NNow if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Mom ran out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit ogling her, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is one great outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That pervert\Ndidn't even glance at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's not his type?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kaneshiro-{\i1}san{\i0}, Room 2001...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Hayashi\NShizue-{\i1}san {\i0}isn't with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Time to\Ndo some investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! You've had too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are you after\Nthe computer virus too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Conan Edogawa from Room 1902.\NDo you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From whom did you hear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people on the tour\Nkeep talking about a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know\Nwhy they're talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All they should know is\Nthat it's the 'ultimate program'...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was once a mysterious\Ncomputer virus that infected
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,computers at large corporations\Nand ravaged all the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, it is an unstoppable\Nand undetectable 'perfect program.'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it was so elusive\Nthat the people named it--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who knows\Ncomputers knows its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And the tour organizer\Nis also named the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that gives some idea as to\Nthe contents of the program!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that name\Nbrings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of my son\Nwho died four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Bye, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Shizue-{\i1}san{\i0}.\NThat lad is one sharp rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Konno-{\i1}san {\i0}from Room 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what he's talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Ebara Tokio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebara Tokio? That old pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was the hacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hacker?! A person\Nwho steals computer data?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes. And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want one of these someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name of my\Nmother who died last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Satomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's named his\NPC after his dead mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That pervert's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where the\Nperson who was sitting here went?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went back to his\Nroom to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if you know him,\Ncould you return this to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nhe had this around his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!\NYou're always sneaking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of them\Nwent to their rooms long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like Dad isn't back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right, you flirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you've\Nhad too much to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says I was eyeing the waitress...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go up to the\Ntop lounge until she cools off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come too, Ran-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Observation Lounge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but not nearly as pretty as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just teasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the ocean's pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oceans sure are creepy at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you first meet Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid. I was\Nbest friends with her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died three years ago, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s brother passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like everyone else here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}. Where\Ndid your dad go anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him earlier with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo-{\i1}san {\i0}from Room 2102, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot about that other old pervert...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:26.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Hotel 2F Pub Emerald
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you were married...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I divorced three years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would anyone\Ndivorce such a beautiful woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, could you tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who the\NNight Baron is by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you!\NThe hotel fee is at stake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! At least a hint!\NPlease, Mr. Great Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be one fun night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess I should\Nget back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko should be cooled off by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus I'd get bitten if\NI stay with you any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...By your little bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you know what the virus is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Virus? Like a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of weird question was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect computer virus,\N'Night Baron.'
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With it, one could\Nthreaten banks or corporations
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,out of large sums of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure lots of people\Nwould like to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:22:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is the tour organizer\Ntrying to do by gathering such people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just a game?! Or maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's disturbing that the immortal\NNight Baron would perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did the Night Baron fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.33,0:24:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this knot is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:31.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron Murder Case (The Suspicion)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.87,0:24:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.34,0:24:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron Murder Case (The Suspicion).
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.20,0:24:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.01,0:24:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode Ran-neechan plays a major part.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-chan, why don't you and I—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.61,0:24:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.32,0:24:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
